{"action":"created","issue":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/55748","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/55748/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/55748/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/55748/events","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55748","id":2522089430,"node_id":"PR_kwDOABkWpM57SbWg","number":55748,"title":"skip unnecessary alias-check in `collect(::AbstractArray)` from `copyto!`","user":{"login":"thchr","id":26799210,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2Nzk5MjEw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/26799210?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr","html_url":"https://github.com/thchr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":115858,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMTU4NTg=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/performance","name":"performance","color":"d7e102","default":false,"description":"Must go faster"},{"id":62693664,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw2MjY5MzY2NA==","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/arrays","name":"arrays","color":"006b75","default":false,"description":"[a, r, r, a, y, s]"}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2024-09-12T11:09:12Z","updated_at":"2024-10-11T07:05:23Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/55748","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55748","diff_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55748.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55748.patch","merged_at":null},"body":"As discussed on Slack with @MasonProtter & @jakobnissen, `collect` currently does a usually cheap - but sometimes expensive - aliasing check (via `unalias`->`mightalias`->`dataid` -> `objectid`) before copying contents over; this check is unnecessary, however, since the source array is newly created and cannot possibly alias the input.
This PR fixes that by swapping from `copyto!` to `copyto_unaliased!` in the `_collect_indices` implementations where the swap is straightforward (e.g., it is not so straightforward for the fallback `_collect_indices(indsA, A)`, so I skipped it there).

This improves the following example substantially:
```jl
struct GarbageVector{N} <: AbstractVector{Int}
    v :: Vector{Int}
    garbage :: NTuple{N, Int}
end
GarbageVector{N}(v::Vector{Int}) where N = GarbageVector{N}(v, ntuple(identity, Val(N)))
Base.getindex(gv::GarbageVector, i::Int) = gv.v[i]
Base.size(gv::GarbageVector) = size(gv.v)

using BenchmarkTools
v = rand(Int, 10)
gv = GarbageVector{100}(v)
@btime collect($v);  # 30 ns (v1.10.4)  -> 30 ns (PR)
@btime collect($gv); # 179 ns (v1.10.4) -> 30 ns (PR)
```

Relatedly, it seems the fact that `mightalias` is comparing immutable contents as well - and hence slowing down the `unalias` check for the above `GarbageVector` via a slow `objectid` on tuples - is suboptimal. I don't know how to fix that though, so I'd like to leave that outside this PR. (Probably related to https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/26237)","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/55748/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/55748/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2406686680","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/55748#issuecomment-2406686680","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/55748","id":2406686680,"node_id":"IC_kwDOABkWpM6Pcx_Y","user":{"login":"thchr","id":26799210,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2Nzk5MjEw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/26799210?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr","html_url":"https://github.com/thchr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thchr/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2024-10-11T07:05:21Z","updated_at":"2024-10-11T07:05:21Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"Bump; I think this is not likely to be very controversial.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2406686680/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null}}

